flavor_text_entries.red:
It was created by
a scientist after
years of horrific gene splicing and
DNA engineering
experiments.
flavor_text_entries.blue:
It was created by

flavor_text_entries.yellow:
Its DNA is almost
the same as MEW's.
However, its size and disposition
are vastly dif­
ferent.
flavor_text_entries.gold:
Because its battle
abilities were
raised to the ultimate level, it
thinks only of de­
feating its foes.
flavor_text_entries.silver:
It usually remains
motionless to con­
serve energy, so that it may un­
leash its full
power in battle.
flavor_text_entries.crystal:
Said to rest qui­
etly in an
undiscovered cave, this POKéMON was
created solely for
battling.
flavor_text_entries.ruby:
MEWTWO is a POKéMON that was created
by genetic manipulation.
However, even though the scientific power of humans created this POKéMON’s
body, they failed to endow MEWTWO with
a compassionate heart.

flavor_text_entries.emerald:
A POKéMON that was created by genetic
manipulation. However, even though the
scientific power of humans made its body,
they failed to give it a warm heart.
flavor_text_entries.firered:
A POKéMON whose genetic code was
repeatedly recombined for research.
It turned vicious as a result.

MEW’s genes. It’s said to have the
most savage heart among Pokémon.
